  "name": "RPlog_Aftermath_of_the_Crashlanding",
  "title": "Aftermath of the Crashlanding",
  "summary": "After crash-landing a stolen ship into the Imperial Embassy on Caspar, the Selas wanderer Simon and his young guide Mira flee on foot into the crowded Fountain Square of Plaxton City. As emergency crews, police, and CDU military under Sub Lieutenant Renovo Shadowlin swarm the chaotic scene and begin a coordinated manhunt for the two lightsaber-wielding fugitives, the Rodian bounty hunter Detjin silently stalks Simon through the press of onlookers. Sensing the predator through the True Source, Simon nearly draws his weapon but instead lashes out at a bystander to create a diversion when Renovo shouts for him to halt. Renovo is pulled away by an urgent crisis with the unstable crashed ship, buying Simon a crucial opening. Simon slips through the mob and rejoins Mira at the cover of her alley, the bounty hunter still in pursuit.",
